    • Method Detail

      • getStrengthMachine

        private Machine getStrengthMachine()
        Handles a complex range of strength representations for the discovery of the combined quantity and unit value for this element. The following represents the range of strength types which are discovered:
        1. 250-mg
        2. two-puffs
        3. 1-cc
        4. 15.5 mg
        5. 25.7-30.2 mg

      • getStrengthCombinedMachine

        private Machine getStrengthCombinedMachine()
        Handles a complex range of strength representations for the discovery of the combined quantity and unit value for this element. The following represents the range of strength types which are discovered:

        2. 1-cc
        3. 0.4mg
        4. two-3.5mg
